channel.title: Help please
channel.description:
Whats a good server base to start on?
I don't really want a server that has all the silly stuff like 125 stats and "super rings" that make you hit over 1000. I just want a normal plan server that i can start on myself and make it more "realistic" then a fantasy server. If anyone could please link me or name one to me I'll appreciate it.
Thanks.
